---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/home.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="PicFast — 自托管图片托管服务" lang="zh">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none">
          <path d="M2 7L5.5 10.5L12 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        开源 · MIT 协议
      </div>
      <h1>你的图片<br />你的服务器<br />完全掌控</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        几分钟内部署一套完整的图床服务。
        无追踪、无限制、无第三方依赖。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-code">
        <div class="code-label">
          <span class="dot red"></span>
          <span class="dot yellow"></span>
          <span class="dot green"></span>
          <span class="code-filename">terminal</span>
        </div>
        <pre><code><span class="prompt">$</span> git clone https://github.com/atbeta/picfast.git
<span class="prompt">$</span> cd picfast
<span class="prompt">$</span> cp .env.example .env
<span class="prompt">$</span> cp config.example.yaml config.yaml
<span class="prompt">$</span> make docker-up</code></pre>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/zh/docs/getting-started" class="btn btn-primary">快速开始</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/atbeta/picfast" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M8 0C3.58 0 0 3.58 0 8c0 3.54 2.29 6.53 5.47 7.59.4.07.55-.17.55-.38 0-.19-.01-.82-.01-1.49-2.01.37-2.53-.49-2.69-.94-.09-.23-.48-.94-.82-1.13-.28-.15-.68-.52-.01-.53.63-.01 1.08.58 1.23.82.72 1.21 1.87.87 2.33.66.07-.52.28-.87.51-1.07-1.78-.2-3.64-.89-3.64-3.95 0-.87.31-1.59.82-2.15-.08-.2-.36-1.02.08-2.12 0 0 .67-.21 2.2.82.64-.18 1.32-.27 2-.27.68 0 1.36.09 2 .27 1.53-1.04 2.2-.82 2.2-.82.44 1.1.16 1.92.08 2.12.51.56.82 1.27.82 2.15 0 3.07-1.87 3.75-3.65 3.95.29.25.54.73.54 1.48 0 1.07-.01 1.93-.01 2.2 0 .21.15.46.55.38A8.013 8.013 0 0016 8c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8z"/>
          </svg>
          GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">功能完整，轻量运行</h2>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
              <rect x="2" y="4" width="18" height="14" rx="2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75"/>
              <path d="M2 8l6 4 4-3 8 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <circle cx="7" cy="7" r="1.5" fill="currentColor"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>API 优先设计</h3>
          <p>完整的 REST API + OpenAPI 规范文档。支持 curl、ShareX 或任何 HTTP 客户端上传。无供应商锁定，可集成到任意工作流。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
              <path d="M11 2L3 6v6c0 5.25 3.4 10.15 8 11.4 4.6-1.25 8-6.15 8-11.4V6L11 2z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M8 11l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>隐私优先</h3>
          <p>无追踪、无分析、无广告。图片只存在你自己的服务器上。可选内容审核机制，你来决定什么能上传。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
              <path d="M4 4h14v14H4z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M4 8h14M8 8v10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>多种存储后端</h3>
          <p>本地文件系统、S3、OSS、COS、Kodo、WebDAV。切换存储后端不影响已有图片。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
              <path d="M4 12h14M4 6h14M4 18h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>开发者体验</h3>
          <p>OpenAPI 文档支持在线调试，内置 ShareX 支持，多格式链接输出（URL、Markdown、BBCode、HTML）。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
              <path d="M11 3v4M11 15v4M3 11H7M15 11h4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>AI / MCP 集成</h3>
          <p>内置 MCP 服务器，AI 助手可通过标准化协议直接上传和管理图片。适合接入各类 AI Agent 工作流。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
              <rect x="3" y="3" width="16" height="16" rx="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75"/>
              <path d="M7 11h8M7 7h8M7 15h5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>现代技术栈</h3>
          <p>Go 后端 + React 前端。一条命令 Docker Compose 启动。PostgreSQL 持久化，内置 Prometheus 指标和 Mailpit 邮件测试。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="comparison">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">与同类方案对比</h2>
      <div class="table-wrapper">
        <table>
          <thead><tr><th></th><th>Chevereto</th><th>Photoview</th><th>自建 S3</th><th>PicFast</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>部署时间</td><td>约 30 分钟</td><td>约 20 分钟</td><td>约 2 小时</td><td><strong>约 5 分钟</strong></td></tr>
            <tr><td>API 支持</td><td>基础</td><td>有限</td><td>自定义</td><td><strong>OpenAPI + 在线文档</strong></td></tr>
            <tr><td>ShareX 集成</td><td>✅</td><td>❌</td><td>自定义</td><td><strong>✅ 内置</strong></td></tr>
            <tr><td>存储后端</td><td>有限</td><td>仅本地</td><td>仅 S3</td><td><strong>6 种后端</strong></td></tr>
            <tr><td>内容审核</td><td>❌</td><td>❌</td><td>自定义</td><td><strong>✅ 内置</strong></td></tr>
            <tr><td>AI / MCP 集成</td><td>❌</td><td>❌</td><td>❌</td><td><strong>✅ 内置</strong></td></tr>
            <tr><td>缩略图生成</td><td>✅</td><td>✅</td><td>自定义</td><td><strong>✅ 自动</strong></td></tr>
            <tr><td>图片处理</td><td>基础</td><td>有限</td><td>自定义</td><td><strong>✅ 压缩 + 水印</strong></td></tr>
            <tr><td>开源</td><td>付费</td><td>✅</td><td>N/A</td><td><strong>✅ MIT</strong></td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="quick-start">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">快速开始</h2>
      <div class="quick-start-grid">
        <div class="qs-step">
          <div class="qs-num">1</div>
          <div class="qs-content">
            <h3>克隆并配置</h3>
            <p>克隆仓库，复制配置文件并修改为自己的设置。</p>
            <div class="hero-code small"><pre><code>git clone https://github.com/atbeta/picfast.git
cd picfast
cp .env.example .env
cp config.example.yaml config.yaml
$EDITOR config.yaml</code></pre></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="qs-step">
          <div class="qs-num">2</div>
          <div class="qs-content">
            <h3>启动服务</h3>
            <p>一条命令同时启动 PostgreSQL、Mailpit（本地邮件测试工具）和应用。</p>
            <div class="hero-code small"><pre><code>make docker-up</code></pre></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="qs-step">
          <div class="qs-num">3</div>
          <div class="qs-content">
            <h3>通过 API 上传</h3>
            <p>注册账号、获取 token，然后上传第一张图片。</p>
            <div class="hero-code small"><pre><code>curl -X POST http://localhost:18080/api/v1/auth/register \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '&#123;"email":"you@example.com","password":"hunter2","name":"You"&#125;'

curl -X POST http://localhost:18080/api/v1/images \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" \
  -F "file=@image.png"</code></pre></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="qs-cta"><a href="/zh/docs/getting-started" class="btn btn-primary">完整文档 →</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
